<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>C Law 2025 - Demos</title>
    
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-black: #000000;
            --text-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --text-gray: #666666;
            --text-light: #999999;
            --background: #ffffff;
            --surface: #f8f9fa;
            --border: #e5e5e5;
            --accent: #333333;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: var(--background);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        /* Logo */
        .logo-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .logo-img {
            height: clamp(40px, 8vw, 60px);
            width: auto;
        }

        /* Welcome Message */
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 3vw, 1.375rem);
            color: var(--text-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Steps Section */
        .steps-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .step {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-black);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }

        .step:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.15);
        }

        .step:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .step h3 {
            font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .step h3::before {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary-black);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .step-1 h3::before { content: "1"; }
        .step-2 h3::before { content: "2"; }
        .step-3 h3::before { content: "3"; }

        .step p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-left: 3rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { 
                opacity: 0; 
                transform: translateY(30px); 
            }
            to { 
                opacity: 1; 
                transform: translateY(0); 
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .step {
            animation: slideInUp 0.6s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .step-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .step-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .step-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 0.5rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 5vh;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
            }

            .logo-section {
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .welcome-message {
                margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            }

            .steps-section {
                margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            }

            .step {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            }

            .step h3::before {
                width: 28px;
                height: 28px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                margin-right: 0.875rem;
            }

            .step p {
                margin-left: 2.375rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 0.25rem;
                padding-top: 3vh;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 0.5rem;
            }

            .logo-section {
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            .welcome-message {
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .steps-section {
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .step {
                padding: 1.25rem;
                border-radius: 12px;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .step h3::before {
                width: 24px;
                height: 24px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                margin-right: 0.75rem;
            }

            .step p {
                margin-left: 1.875rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 769px) {
            body {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 3rem 2rem;
            }

            .logo-section {
                margin-bottom: 4rem;
            }

            .welcome-message {
                margin-bottom: 4rem;
            }

            .steps-section {
                margin-bottom: 4rem;
            }

            .step {
                padding: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .step h3::before {
                width: 36px;
                height: 36px;
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-right: 1.25rem;
            }

            .step p {
                margin-left: 3.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1200px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 700px;
                padding: 4rem 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container fade-in">
        <!-- 1. Logo -->
        <div class="logo-section">
            <img src="https://www.tela.com/_vercel/image?url=%2Ftela-logo.png&w=320&q=100" alt="Tela Logo" class="logo-img">
        </div>
        
        <!-- 2. Mensagem de boas-vindas -->
        <div class="welcome-message">
            Bem-vindos ao portal de demos do Tela.<br>
            Use os QR codes disponíveis no estande para acessar as demonstrações escolhidas.
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Passo a passo -->
        <div class="steps-section">
            <div class="step step-1">
                <h3>Escaneie o QR Code</h3>
                <p>Use a câmera do seu smartphone para escanear o código da demonstração desejada.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step step-2">
                <h3>Faça login com LinkedIn</h3>
                <p>Clique em "Acessar com LinkedIn" e autorize o acesso aos seus dados básicos.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step step-3">
                <h3>Assista à demonstração</h3>
                <p>Após o login, você será redirecionado para a demonstração exclusiva.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Copyright -->
        <div class="footer">
            © 2025 Tela. Todos os direitos reservados.
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Animação de entrada
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            document.querySelector('.container').classList.add('fade-in');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html> 